            "title": "半日收市︱科股領跑 恒指升115點報26633點 紫金又創新高膺藍籌最強",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">颶風過後，港股今早在重磅科股領跑下再升，主板半日成交增至1757.57億元。銅價揚升帶動金屬板塊，紫金礦業(02899)再登藍籌升幅榜首。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：紫金礦業官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250115_FI_source-web_02899-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：紫金礦業官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250115_FI_source-web_02899-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：紫金礦業官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數輕微高開17點後，初段曾經歷反覆爭持階段，一度倒跌94點，低見26423點，直至中段時波幅大致維持在升跌約50點的窄幅範圍，於上午約11時左右重現動力，將升幅逐步擴大，最高衝上26640點，升121點；恒指中午收報26633點，升115點或0.43%。</p>\n<!-- slider begin -->\n<div class=\"fancy-slider\">\n<p class=\"fancy-gallery-tips\" style=\"font-weight: bold;font-size: 18px; margin: 0\">點擊看圖輯</p>\n<div class=\"fancy-main\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：紫金礦業官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250115_FI_source-web_02899-2.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：紫金礦業官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250115_FI_source-web_02899-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：紫金礦業官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"巴士的報記者攝\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_FI_source-web_00388-1.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"巴士的報記者攝\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_FI_source-web_00388-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">巴士的報記者攝</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"紫金礦業官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/02899.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"紫金礦業官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/02899.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">紫金礦業官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：京東官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250218_FI_source-web_09618.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：京東官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250218_FI_source-web_09618.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：京東官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<a class=\"fancy-main__slide\" data-caption=\"華虹半導體官網\" data-fancybox=\"slider-gallery\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/01347-2.jpg.webp\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__image\">\n<img alt=\"華虹半導體官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/01347-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-main__title bpcategory-special-color\">華虹半導體官網</h3>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__controls-text bpcategory-special-color\">更多相片</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__buttons\">\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __prev fancy-main-prev\" style=\"border-right: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n<div class=\"rule\"></div>\n<div class=\"fancy-main__button __next fancy-main-next\" style=\"border-left: 8px solid #996600\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs\">\n<div class=\"swiper-wrapper\">\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：紫金礦業官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250115_FI_source-web_02899-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：紫金礦業官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"巴士的報記者攝\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_FI_source-web_00388-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">巴士的報記者攝</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"紫金礦業官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/02899.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">紫金礦業官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：京東官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250218_FI_source-web_09618.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">圖片來源：京東官網</h3>\n</div>\n<div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n<div class=\"fancy-thumbs__image\">\n<img alt=\"華虹半導體官網\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/01347-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"h3 fancy-thumbs__title bpcategory-special-color\">華虹半導體官網</h3>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<!-- slider end -->\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數今早非但幾乎全程報升，表現更明顯跑贏大市，半日升120點或1.91%，報6443點；國企指數56 點或0.6%，報9499點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指半日升158點，報26642點，高水8點。科指期貨升136點，報6447點，高水3點。國指期貨升79點，報9506點，高水7點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"巴士的報記者攝\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_FI_source-web_00388-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"巴士的報記者攝\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_FI_source-web_00388-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">巴士的報記者攝</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">近期金價屢創新高，已推動一眾金礦股揚升，美國礦業巨擘Freeport-McMoRan宣布旗下印尼Grasberg礦場(全球第二大銅礦)的合約供應觸發不可抗力條款，並指第3季度銅和黃金綜合銷售預計將下降，則引發銅價急升。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"紫金礦業官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/02899.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"紫金礦業官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/02899.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">紫金礦業官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">金屬板塊今早乘勢炒上，紫金飆6.28%，報31.5元，再創歷史新高；洛陽鉬業(03993)亦破頂，飆13.33%，報14.2元；江西銅業(00358)也升8.71%，報26.96元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">重磅科股更是今早升市的火車頭，AI概念近年成為驅動科企股價的主要引擎。京東(09618)首席執行官許冉在「2025京東全球科技探索者大會」上表示，京東將在AI技術上持續加碼，目標是帶動各個產業及行業，形成萬億元人民幣規模的AI生態。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">他又透露，京東創始人劉強東會親自擔任京東探索研究院院長，並在全球招募頂尖科學家加入京東，集團同時會與多間高校開展合作，創建共享實驗室。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：京東官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250218_FI_source-web_09618.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：京東官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/20250218_FI_source-web_09618.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：京東官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">京東今早高開1.88%後一直維持強勢，早市中段更顯著抽升，一度升上142.6元，漲7.22%；中午收報141.2點，仍升8.2元或6.17%，創3個月高位，在藍籌升幅榜排名僅略遜於紫金而位列次席。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">其餘重磅科股亦升多跌少，百度(09888)揚升4.36%，報134.2元；獲瑞銀唱好，將目標價定在95.37元的快手(01024)，也升2.86%，報79.05元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">小米(01810)今天傍晚舉行小米17系列新品發布會，股價今早率先助慶，升3.6%，報58.95元；騰訊(00700)則升1.47%，報658元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">日前表示擬於3年投資3800億元人幣發展AI的阿里巴巴(09988)，股價經昨天急漲9%後，今早略為回氣，但也升0.46%，報174.8元，逭近期相對弱勢的美團(03690)亦反覆升0.59%，報102.8元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">芯片股亦持續強勢，早前已創歷史新高的中芯國際(00981)，今早升1.82%，報78.15元；華虹半導體(01347)接力破頂，報67.3元，漲6.4%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"華虹半導體官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/01347-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"華虹半導體官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/11/01347-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">華虹半導體官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">相反，金融股則有壓力，建設銀行(00939)見3個月低位，報7.33元，跌1.87%；工商銀行(01398)更跌2.07%，報5.69元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">據報滙控(00005)要求旗下恒生銀行(00011)處理香港地產不良貸款，兩股今早均逆市偏軟；滙控跌0.65%，報106.8元；恒生更跌2.2%，報115.6元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">奇瑞汽車(09973)今日登場，中午收報33.38元，較招股價30.75元高8.55%。市傳內地電動車企阿維塔來港IPO準備工作已進入後期，有望10月遞交申請，目標明年第3季上市，集資規模達10億美元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">持阿維塔14.1%的寧德時代(03750)今早已率先A、H齊創新高，H股中午收報533元，漲5.34%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15292707-%e5%8d%8a%e6%97%a5%e6%94%b6%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e7%a7%91%e8%82%a1%e9%a0%98%e8%b7%91-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%87115%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b126633%e9%bb%9e-%e7%b4%ab%e9%87%91%e5%8f%88%e5%89%b5%e6%96%b0%e9%ab%98",
