        {
            "title": "A股低開高走，深股升逾1%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">A股先跌後升，深成旨升逾1%，兩市成交合計15428.95億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"A股 AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250407_FI_source-ap_China_Trump_Tariffs_25097181957222-4.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"A股 AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250407_FI_source-ap_China_Trump_Tariffs_25097181957222-4.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">A股 AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證綜指半日升5點或0.16%，報3859點，今早以3852點開市，跌1點或0.03%，中段低見3844，跌9點或0.23%，其後向上，最高見3861點，升8點或0.21%，為半日高位，半日成交6461.26億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指半日升152點或1.14%，報13508點，今早開市報13333點，亦跌23點或0.17%，早段低見13295，跌61點或0.46%，後段穩步向上，最高見13516，升160點或1.2%。半日成交8967.69億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數半日報4607，升41點或0.9%，今早開跌2點，開報4563點；</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">創業板指數半日報3256，升70點或2.22%，今早開市報3167點，跌17點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15292465-a%e8%82%a1%e4%bd%8e%e9%96%8b%e9%ab%98%e8%b5%b0%ef%bc%8c%e6%b7%b1%e8%82%a1%e5%8d%87%e9%80%be1",
